snippet: Travis d'Arnaud hit a go-ahead RBI double in the eighth inning to lift the New York Mets to a 4-3 win over the Miami Marlins on Wednesday night....

headline.print_headline: D'Arnaud's RBI Double Lifts Mets Over Marlins 4-3
headline.main: D'Arnaud's RBI Double Lifts Mets Over Marlins 4-3

lead_paragraph: Travis d'Arnaud hit a go-ahead RBI double in the eighth inning to lift the New York Mets to a 4-3 win over the Miami Marlins on Wednesday night.
